{
  "stem": "10181.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "They-- This went on till May 1940.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Now, I remember the date.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "That's one of the few dates I remember exactly because it sort of-- it was a milestone.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was May 10, 1940.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "May's a beautiful month in Holland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "In Holland, you have a lot of rain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "But May usually is no rain and a lot of sun.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "It was a sunny day, May 10, 1940.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And I woke up, and it was very noisy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "I could hear like a lot of planes in the sky, a lot of noise.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "We lived by a main road.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "A lot of noise on the road.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "In those days, there weren't many cars.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, it sounded like a whole army was down there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And it was.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "When I got up and looked out the window, I saw the German army.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And tanks, and-- and trucks, and whatever.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And opposite us was a large, sort of empty place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "Empty-- big, empty place which was used for fairs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "You know, for-- once a year, there was-- in-- in German Dutch, they call it [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "It's like a fair, you know, with-- with all sort of things.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And it was empty, so there were trucks and tanks parked there already.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And a lot of planes in the sky.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "These were German planes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was-- so like, what's going on?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, and the Germans had invaded Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when I came downstairs, my uncle was gone because he knew that they would be looking for him very soon.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When my aunt was making coffee, a German soldier knocked on the door and very civilly, you know, very nicely had asked-- he brought some coffee with him.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Could she make some coffee for him, and-- and-- which she said, why not?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he asked me to look at-- stand at the window to watch whether his unit was leaving, I should tell him, you know, so that he wouldn't miss his-- his truck or whatever he was with.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he sat there, drunk his coffee, didn't say very much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- said, thank you very much and walked out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the next few days, like we-- like all other kids, we went to the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they had sort of like an encampment, you know, where they-- where they had the army.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we-- to-- to see them and-- and-- and their-- sort of-- it was-- it was a fascinating thing in a way for-- for kids.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I do remember-- what I do remember was some Dutch soldiers who had shed their uniform after, you know, when they saw the invasion, and were-- Why do I remember it?",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they all were wearing clothes which didn't fit them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, that's how you could know it was a soldier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because some-- some civilian had given them clothes and they usually didn't fit.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we knew these were soldiers who had been surprised by the invasion and not wanting to be taken prisoner, so they were wearing, you know, ill-fitting civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But we didn't care.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we went to the German camp, and they gave us candy even.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they tried to be nice at the beginning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Especially in-- in-- in Western Europe, especially in Holland, they tried to be civilized.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they-- they considered the Dutch to be kinsmen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there even was an occasion where-- and this is sort of-- I always-- always remember this where-- I don't know whether it was-- I don't think it was-- I think it was just a regular soldier who was giving us candy or something.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one of the boys said to me, you don't want to give it to him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He's a Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, so the soldier turned around to him and said, I didn't ask you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I didn't ask your opinion, you know, which was sort of-- was very strange.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, but at the time, sort of, I took it in stride.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know, I thought it was very nice of him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But this was just the first week or two, you know, when they were that civilized.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, and then-- first of all, after a few days, the Gestapo-- Gestapo is the German secret police.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They knocked on the door to look for my uncle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And of course, he was gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Like he knew-- he knew that they would look for him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had taken his bicycle and had-- took the-- and was going into Holland, deeper into Holland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, he-- he thought maybe he could out-cycle the German army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, like-- like everybody, nobody realized that, you know, that Holland would very quickly capitulate.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
